member.summary:
This method extracts from a JSON string an array of name/value pairs. 
The name of the array must be specified as a parameter. 
E.g.:
    { "Configurations": [{ "DbKey": "db1", "ProjectUid": "U:2:A3BQHFA8AR:", WorkingOverlayID:"Test-Arbeitsschicht", SystemUid:"U:8:A3X0C5WU0D:J5"},
                         { "DbKey": "db6", "ProjectUid": "U:2:A3BQHFA8AR:", WorkingOverlayID:"Test-Arbeitsschicht", SystemUid:"U:8:A3X0C5WU0D:J5"}
                        ],
      "References":     [{ "DbKey": "db1", "ProjectUid": "U:2:A3BQHFA8AR:", WorkingOverlayID:"Test-Arbeitsschicht", SystemUid:"U:8:A3X0C5WU0D:J5"},
                         { "DbKey": "db6", "ProjectUid": "U:2:A3BQHFA8AR:", WorkingOverlayID:"Test-Arbeitsschicht", SystemUid:"U:8:A3X0C5WU0D:J5"}
                        ]                         
    }
